							</header>
							<div class="entry">
								<div class="entry-summary">
									<p>Maids in Singapore can be categorized into two categories, one is transfer maid and another is a new maid who can be hired from an agency. Transfer maids are much in demand as one gets experienced maid who is just being transferred from one employer to another. As per the statistics of the domestic agencies,</p>
