						<article class="post-100051811 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-helper category-skills tag-domestic-helper tag-maid" id="post-100051811">
							<header class="entry-header">
								<a class="entry-header__featured-image" href="https://www.helperplace.com/motivate-retain-trustworthy-helper" rel="bookmark"><span class="overlay"></span> <img alt="Retain a trustworthy helper" class="attachment-content-grid size-content-grid wp-post-image" data-attachment-id="100051834" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-description="" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="Trustworthy helper" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/www.helperplace.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Trustworthy-helper.jpg?fit=540%2C303&amp;ssl=1" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/www.helperplace.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Trustworthy-helper.jpg?fit=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/www.helperplace.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Trustworthy-helper.jpg?fit=540%2C303&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="540,303" data-permalink="https://www.helperplace.com/motivate-retain-trustworthy-helper/trustworthy-helper" height="200" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.helperplace.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Trustworthy-helper.jpg?resize=400%2C200&amp;ssl=1" width="400"></a>
								<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.helperplace.com/motivate-retain-trustworthy-helper" rel="bookmark">Motivate and Retain a Trustworthy Helper</a></h3>
								<div class="entry-meta">
									25 October 2017
								</div>
							</header>
							<div class="entry">
								<div class="entry-summary">
